name: 𝙒𝘼𝙏𝘾𝙃 𝙒𝙃𝘼𝙏 𝙔𝙊𝙐 𝙒𝙄𝙎𝙃 𝙁𝙊𝙍
description:
AnubisFX: "𝙒𝘼𝙏𝘾𝙃 𝙒𝙃𝘼𝙏 𝙔𝙊𝙐 𝙒𝙄𝙎𝙃 𝙁𝙊𝙍"

"𝙒𝘼𝙏𝘾𝙃 𝙒𝙃𝘼𝙏 𝙔𝙊𝙐 𝙒𝙄𝙎𝙃 𝙁𝙊𝙍" is a pretty common saying amongst the wise but have you really thought about it. A lot of what you wish for now is currently out of reach, that’s why you wish for it. Just just imagine you reaching it automatically just by wishing. Would you know what to do with what you wished for without having the experience you use it wisely? Most of the time, without the experience you’d lose whatever you wished for as fast as you’d reach it. The only way to receive what you are wishing for is when you’re ready. When you’ve been beat up left and right with experiences, then you shall be ready to receive from God. Trust in your journey, the pain you receive during your journey is getting you ready for the blessings you’ve been wishing for. Be patient and have faith! God is getting you ready✨
